FBIS3-15005 "drsov041_p_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-041 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Mar 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Russian Troops' Status Still Not Approved NC0103204694 Yerevan SNARK in English 1404 GMT 1 Mar 94 NC0103204694 Yerevan SNARK Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Yerevan, March 1. (SNARK) -- Armenian Liberal Democratic Party called for faster ratification of agreement on legal status of Russian troops in Armenia, signed two years ago. Parliamentary representative of this party Petros Katsakhyan reminded the deputies that the Supreme Council of Russian Federation has already ratified this document exactly a year ago. According to the information made known by the Armenian financial minister Levon Barkhudaryan, nearly 8 billion rubles were allocated in the republican state budget to support the Russian armed contingent.
